title: When you see a fed Malphite as an AD champ

replies.body: then he gets mad because you never give up, never surrender.
This is a reference to what?
It's from Galaxy Quest, where his character is stuck on a planet and has to survive against a rock monster the natives call "Grignak".

"For the love of god I can't get within 1,500 units of him! What do you want me to do?"

"What? Why not?"

"HE'S FULL- " *an ally has been slain*

{{champion:54}} {{item:3001}} {{item:3089}} {{item:3285}} {{item:1026}} {{item:1052}}  "I can finally finish my void staff."
Build zonyas. They wont know what to do when you zonyas their ult E.
Can't you just create some sort of Rudimentary Lathe?

See, when I saw the title of your post, I thought you meant that a fed Malphite went "as an AD champ" i.e. got so fed that he built AD. Well, [that happened to me](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/2212839046/220319014?tab=overview), and let me tell you, it was horrifying.
